cat << EOF
HDDtemp is tool that give you the temperature of your IDE hard drive by reading S.M.A.R.T. informations  (that support this feature). Only moderns hard drives have a temperature sensor. SCSI doesn't allow reading S.M.A.R.T. informations.
EOF
